comment: This bourbon has a great flavor, that whole line of bourbons are great
This bourbon isn't bad, & for the money it's a decent deal. Corn & light caramel with a hint of toffee in the finish, it left me wanting it to be a little bit more.

Nose: Carmel Corn in a Dusty Field, Slight Fruitiness (Trouble Identifying)

Taste: Dust Covered Banana with Apples and a Hit of Black Pepper
